item.description:
&ldquo;This Rick and Morty themed challenge requires you to exploit a webserver to find 3 ingredients that will help Rick make his potion to transform himself back into a human from a pickle.&rdquo;
Hello, this is Neo. Today we have a CTF of Tryhackme - Pickle Rick. Let&rsquo;s get root!!!
Firstly, always, I will scan open port. I use rustscan because it faster than nmap, moreover it can integrates with nmap.
